videos.description: A.J. Turner runs for a 12 yd TD as South Carolina takes a 7-3 lead
videos.headline: South Carolina takes the lead with TD run

videos.description: Stanley Williams goes left and gets through a tackle before turning on the speed to find the end zone from 43 yards out giving Kentucky the lead.
videos.headline: Williams sheds a tackle to go 43 yards for Kentucky TD

videos.description: Stephen Johnson pass intercepted by D.J. Smith
videos.headline: Gamecocks stop Kentucky drive with interception

videos.description: Benjamin Snell Jr. runs for 1 yd TD to give Kentucky a 17-10 lead
videos.headline: Wildcats reclaim lead in 4th Quarter

videos.description: South Carolina's Hayden Hurst makes the catch and tries to go over the defender, but Chris Westry is not fooled and catches Hurst to slam him to the ground.
videos.headline: This is what happens when your hurdle attempt doesn't fool anyone
